::Cygnar::
       He lands on the island and transforms approaching the others.  "I'm 
glad to see you have both made it here and aren't trying to kill each other.  
It would crimp our working relationship if you were.  But now, we need to get 
down to the business at hand.  We all have our separate reasons for being 
here.  You, Rodimus want Galvatron dead.  And, you, Tyrael, want Megatron 
dead.  I want them separated.  I would prefer Galvatron not die, but I am ... 
flexible in that regard."  He looks between the two of them.  "We must 
organize our forces quickly.  And effectively.  Are there any others you 
think should participate in this attack?"

--part1_118.190c0aee.2ad9e0fa_boundary
